full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/18/2023 Central Office 14036/392-A Washington, D. C. -2- Sept. 17, 1948 Place of Birth: Los Angeles, Calif. Citizenship Status: Admitted to United States as a native at San Francisco, Calif., ex SS "PRESIDENT TAFT", October 20, 1926. Residence: (1932) 1135 E. 21st St., Los Angeles, Calif, Mother: GONG SHE E ex iv Age 42 (1932) Natural feet Date and place of birth: KS 17-2-9 (March 18, 1891) in AI LUNG Village, Sun Ning District, China. Wife: FONG SHEE ; natural feet Residence: (1936) Song Lung Village, Hoy San District, China. Children: (As of July 5, 1936) WONG DOON LIM ; male; born CR 23-10-30 (December 6, 1934) WONG DOON CHEE ; male; born CR 25-1-21 (February 13, 1936) Residence of Children: China The records of this office do not contain any information concerning the subject subsequent to July 5, 1936. Identical information was furnished the District Director, Los Angeles, California, on July 8, 1948, for use in processing a petition for an immigration visa (Form I-133) filed by the subject in behalf of his alleged wife, FONG SUEY GEE.
